          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Cross sections of photonuclear reactions with emission",
                "of Ne24 clusters and ranges of these clusters in",
                "policarbonate were measured in the photon energy range",
                "18.-28. MeV. The clusters were detected studying",
                "gamma-radiation of the daughter nucleus Na24. The",
                "energy of the clusters turned out to be 40 MeV. The",
                "probability of their emission by the compound nucleus",
                "at excitation energy of 28. MeV was 5.*10**(-8). The",
                "mechanism of the observed phenomenon was discussed."
              ]
            }
          ],
